<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/9691> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #9691" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/10> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "ref. 518" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7255> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7255" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cos. Suff. 40. Praefectus fabrum of Caesar during his praetorship in 62 and his consulship in 59 (Cic. Balb. 63), perhaps also during his proconsulate in Hisp. Ult. in 61-60. Pro praetore, 41? If the coins with the inscription Balbus Pro Pr refer to him rather than to his nephew (see MRR 2.381), they should date before his consulship. In MRR 2.381, and Index, 550, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.526-527, no. 518, 41 B.C., who rejects the possibility of an issue in Spain.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6269> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6269" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Coins, probably from Hither Spain, name a Balbus Pro Pr. (Grueber, CRRBM 2.406f., with attribution to Gaul) who may perhaps be identified with the # (Legate) who was in Spain in 40 B. C. (App. BC 5.54). If the elder Balbus is referred to, the position preceded his consulship, if the younger, no more is known of his activities for some years (see RE no. 69, article by Münzer, and no. 70, article by Groag; PIR² 2.311, no. 1331, Groag; and Ganter 14; cf. also below, Legates, on C. Livius)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6257> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6257" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Sacerd., CIL 12.1, p. 60, no. III-ILS 9338, no. 3; Fast. Colot., Degrassi 273-275; Fast. Mag. Vic., ibid. 282, 287; Fast. Biond., ibid. 291f.; ibid. 135, 504f.; and on Balbus, CIL 10.3854-ILS 888; Plin. NH 7.136; Dio 48.32.2." .
